AddressFamily inet
Port 22
HostKey /etc/ssh/ssh_host_ed25519_key
KexAlgorithms sntrup761x25519-sha512@openssh.com,curve25519-sha256,curve25519-sha256@libssh.org,ecdh-sha2-nistp521,ecdh-sha2-nistp384,ecdh-sha2-nistp256
Ciphers chacha20-poly1305@openssh.com,aes256-gcm@openssh.com
MACs hmac-sha2-512-etm@openssh.com,hmac-sha2-512,hmac-sha2-256-etm@openssh.com,hmac-sha2-256
AuthenticationMethods publickey
LogLevel VERBOSE
PermitRootLogin no
Banner /etc/issue.net
X11Forwarding no
